rows.label: tlk41400011_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm something of an economist,
and I think everyone should engage
in more consumer activity.

rows.label: tlk41400011_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Whether you're buying or selling,
as long as money is circulating,
the economy will too.

rows.label: tlk41400011_01_msg0004
rows.name:
And if that happens,
this city will develop.

rows.label: tlk41400011_01_msg0005
rows.name: And what happens when it develops?

rows.label: tlk41400011_01_msg0006
rows.name:
You'll be able to buy
things cheaper than now.
